com.facebook.buck.core.sourcepath.resolver.impl

Class AbstractSourcePathResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.core.sourcepath.resolver.impl.AbstractSourcePathResolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SourcePathResolver
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultSourcePathResolver

    public abstract class AbstractSourcePathResolver
extends Object
implements SourcePathResolver
    Abstract implementation of SourcePathResolver.

    Most of the SourcePathResolver interface can be implemented in terms of just a few functions ( the main requirement is resolving BuildTargetSourcePaths).
